            <title>[THRIFT-2388] GoLang - Fix data races in simple_server and server_socket</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-2388</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The documentation for Interrupt() on server_transport states that implementations of Interrupt() should be thread safe, but the implementation in server_socket.go is not.&lt;/p&gt;

